# Tagging OPUS files
Use kid3-cli:

kid3-cli -c "set album 'Album Name'" -c "set artist Artist" -c "set genre 'Genre'" -c "set date Year" *.opus
kid3-cli -c "set track #" -c "set title 'Title'" file.opus

# Set album art
kid3-cli -c "set picture:./path_to_album_art.jpg 'Description of picture'" *.opus
